Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  亲爱的\N{\fs12}Hey, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可能更糟糕的\N{\fs12}It could be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道会怎样  但情况也许比现在更糟\N{\fs12}I don't know how, but it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前常去这家披萨店\N{\fs12}So I used to go to this pizza parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你在这过生日的话  他们可能会把派拍你脸上\N{\fs12}There, when it was your birthday, they would give you a... a pie in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有时候就是会做这么无聊的事\N{\fs12}But they would do this cheap thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有时候也会把剃须膏抹在纸盘子上\N{\fs12}where they would put shaving cream on a paper plate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,然后拍到你的脸上\N{\fs12}and then smear it on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很有意思  - 是的\N{\fs12}- Nice. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,之前有一次因为吃了薄荷  我得了皮疹\N{\fs12}And, of course, I got a rash from the menthol.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而且那天和我约会的那个家伙  实在是倒胃口\N{\fs12}And the guy that I was on the date with, it was really embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好像叫劳伦斯还是什么的\N{\fs12}His name was Lawrence or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他说我闻起来像个男人\N{\fs12}He said I smelled like a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗  - 是啊\N{\fs12}- Huh. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,之后大家都在狂笑\N{\fs12}And everybody laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是有点糗\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀孕了\N{\fs12}I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我说我怀孕了\N{\fs12}I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我拿着  我做了测验\N{\fs12}Hold this. I have the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  我测了两次  好吧  到光下面来\N{\fs12}l... I did it twice and... well, come in the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了吗  两次都是两条红线\N{\fs12}See? Both times the pink line goes all the way across.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说  我怀孕了\N{\fs12}So... I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你  你想要这个吗\N{\fs12}ls this... is this what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:01:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想不想要一个孩子吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- Do I want to be pregnant? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我当然不想\N{\fs12}No. No, I don't want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们到底在谈什么呢\N{\fs12}What are we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  这并不是我是想的样子  你明白吗\N{\fs12}Well, look, it's not exactly the way l imagined it would happen, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  所以你想怎么做\N{\fs12}Right. So what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不知道  尼克\N{\fs12}I don't know, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那  你准备好做一个父亲了吗\N{\fs12}Well, do you want to be a father?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
