Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有个无家可归的家伙  弗雷迪 · 墨菲\N{\fs12}This homeless guy... Fred Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直在整个城市到处涂鸦信任两个字\N{\fs12}He's been painting ''Believe'' all over the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,信任\N{\fs12}''Believe.''
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,医院  犯罪现场  房屋中介\N{\fs12}Hospitals. Crime scenes. Housing projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他四处奔波想要努力传递一点希望\N{\fs12}He goes and tries to spread a little hope around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这种行为  说不清楚  很鼓舞人心吧\N{\fs12}lt's, uh... I don't know... it's very... inspirational.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样  这是艾滋病救济联盟主席  维多利亚·里特尔小姐\N{\fs12}Anyway... this is Victoria Little, Chairman of the AIDS Relief Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好\N{\fs12}Hi, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,由于艾滋病人徒步活动因雨取消\N{\fs12}Uh... when the, uh, AIDS Walk was rained out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,艾滋病救济联盟损失了百分之三十的运营预算\N{\fs12}the AIDS Relief Alliance lost thirty percent of their operating budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经减少了很多计划  甚至包括法律服务的开支\N{\fs12}They've already cut several of their programs, including their legal services.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我和阿尔文最终决定\N{\fs12}Right. And Alvin and I have decided
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,使用郡政府的补助  来为他们的客户辩护\N{\fs12}to use some of our county funds to represent their clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便说一下  即将会有一个强制性的艾滋病意识培训研讨会\N{\fs12}So, by the way, there will be a mandatory AIDS Awareness Training Seminar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,从今天起  为期一周\N{\fs12}a week from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会在这一周一直在这里答疑\N{\fs12}And I'll be here all week to answer any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  我们这周六正举行紧急筹款活动\N{\fs12}Also, we're having an emergency fundraiser this Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,会在焦油坑俱乐部举行一场假面舞会\N{\fs12}lt's a masquerade party at The Tar Pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是一家几个月之前倒闭了的俱乐部\N{\fs12}lt's this club that closed a few months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,也是为了减少一些徒步活动造成的损失\N{\fs12}lt's to recover some of the losses from the walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,并且  各位可以带一个客人来参加  免费的\N{\fs12}And, uh... you and a guest are invited... free of charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  请带上你们的朋友们  尽量说服他们捐款\N{\fs12}So please bring your friends, but make them pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,信任\N{\fs12}''Believe.''
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你们大家应该看一看这篇文章\N{\fs12}You guys, you gotta see this article.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,信任  是吧\N{\fs12}''Believe''... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有个家伙把这个涂得到处都是\N{\fs12}The guy's painting it everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\fs12}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我觉得这是一次机会\N{\fs12}So I think it's an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  难道你想让我们去画这个家伙的标志吗\N{\fs12}What, you want us to print this guy's symbol?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们现在有一个很好的机会  摆脱困境\N{\fs12}Well, you guys are in an ideal position to get it out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们马上要破产了  - 快别再提这个了\N{\fs12}- We're about to go belly-up. - Get it out there fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  还有其他的商人屯了七万五千个马克杯  T恤\N{\fs12}I mean, what other merchandiser's got seventy-five thousand mugs, T-shirts,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还有钥匙链在那积灰吗\N{\fs12}and key chains sitting around collecting dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们即使不用那个标志也可以\N{\fs12}Yeah, well, we can move those units without a symbol on 'em
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,赚到二十万\N{\fs12}for two hundred grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那是批发\N{\fs12}That's wholesale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果印上信任这个想法成功了  可能就会价值数百万\N{\fs12}But if this ''Believe'' idea works, it could be worth... millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  关于印刷的费用呢\N{\fs12}Nah. What about printing costs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那能多少钱啊  一件十美分\N{\fs12}What's it gonna be, ten cents a unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,每件十美分的话我们就得借钱了\N{\fs12}Ten cents a unit we'd have to borrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我们摆脱债务才是当前要务\N{\fs12}Thought the idea was to get out of debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,信任\N{\fs12}''Believe''?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,t恤衫\N{\fs12}T-shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,帽子\N{\fs12}Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,钥匙链\N{\fs12}Key chains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fs12}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在忙吗  - 没有  请坐\N{\fs12}- You busy? - No. No. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗  - 挺好  你呢\N{\fs12}- You okay? - Fine. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还不错\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我在诊所预约了\N{\fs12}l, uh... I made an appointment at a clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,诊所\N{\fs12}Clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  明天早上八点\N{\fs12}Right. Tomorrow morning at 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,诊所吗\N{\fs12}Clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  就是去  你也知道我现在的情况\N{\fs12}Yeah. Just to, you know, see where I'm at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,去验下血  也再考虑一下\N{\fs12}And get a blood test and weigh the options.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那  我明天陪你一起去吧\N{\fs12}Well, uh... l... I'd like to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,早上八点\N{\fs12}lt's at 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你告诉我了  - 嗯  是已经告诉你了\N{\fs12}- You told me. - Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  尼克  -嘿\N{\fs12}- Hi, Nick. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是马库斯 · 小麦和他的妹妹艾塔\N{\fs12}This is Marcus Wheat and his sister Etta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 你好啊\N{\fs12}- Hey. - What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 厉害  - 别急  你也能学会\N{\fs12}- Okay. - Don't worry. You'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  嘿\N{\fs12}Okay. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好吗  - 挺好的\N{\fs12}- How are you? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,马库斯  能带你妹妹出去一下吗\N{\fs12}Marcus, will you take your sister outside for just a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以去我刚刚告诉你们的地方玩玩具  好吗\N{\fs12}You can play with the toys where I showed you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜\N{\fs12}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们需要去找一下达姆森法官\N{\fs12}I think we need to go to Judge Damsen's chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么  - 他们需要一个医疗监护人\N{\fs12}- Why? - They need a medical guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,医疗监护人  怎么会呢\N{\fs12}Medical guardian? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们的妈妈三天之前死于艾滋病  并且她拒绝给孩子们检查\N{\fs12}Their mother died of AIDS three days ago, and she refused to have them tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那阿尔文提到的有争议的捐款又是怎么回事\N{\fs12}So what's this Alvin mentioned about a contested donation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  是我的一个朋友  叫沃伦·康纳\N{\fs12}Well, there's a friend of mine, Warren Connor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他三个月之前死了\N{\fs12}he died three months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,给联盟留下了一百万美金\N{\fs12}and he left the Alliance a million dollars,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他的孩子们对此很不满\N{\fs12}and his kids aren't too happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  那你们需要我来解决这件事吗\N{\fs12}Oh, so do you need me to handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  阿尔文说他认识那个律师\N{\fs12}Well, actually, Alvin said that he knows the lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就是康纳的孩子们的代理律师  所以\N{\fs12}that's representing the Connor kids, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那  有什么我能帮上忙的吗\N{\fs12}Well, uh... is there anything I can do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  有一个叫天梯的俱乐部\N{\fs12}Yes. In fact, there's this club called Lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 表面上是一个男性体育俱乐部  - 是个同性恋俱乐部吗\N{\fs12}- It's ostensibly a sports club for men. - A gay club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个底层的男性\N{\fs12}A place where minority men on the down low
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,和一些生活压抑的白人去的风月场所\N{\fs12}and closeted white guys go for anonymous sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  我能帮上什么呢\N{\fs12}And how can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们希望能有机会给他们进行免费的艾滋病检测  教育和预防\N{\fs12}We want access, to provide free AIDS testing, education, prevention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我没办法接触到他们\N{\fs12}I haven't been able to get anywhere with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我觉得  作为一个律师  也许你能引起他们的注意\N{\fs12}so I thought, since you're a lawyer, you might be able to get their attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\N{\fs12}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就现在吗\N{\fs12}lt's time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  会议二十分钟后开始  伯顿向来很准时\N{\fs12}Yeah. Meeting's in twenty minutes. Burton's very punctual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的妈妈从没给他们做过检查吗\N{\fs12}Their mother never tested them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那他们的爸爸呢\N{\fs12}What about the father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:07:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还在找\N{\fs12}We're still looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,佩尔小姐  要知道你并没有义务\N{\fs12}Miss Pell, you understand you're under no obligation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,去给孩子们做检查\N{\fs12}to have these children tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  你是他们的医疗监护人\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin, you're the medical guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,由你来决定要不要做检查\N{\fs12}lt's up to you to approve the testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  达姆森并没有意见  那我们还等什么\N{\fs12}You know, Damsen might have a point. Why not wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是安置好他们然后再做检查吗\N{\fs12}You mean place them and then test them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  如果他们感染了艾滋  再接受治疗  这样行不通\N{\fs12}Well, if they're infected, they need treatment. It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,行不通吗\N{\fs12}Simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不想把孩子安顿在某个家庭\N{\fs12}I don't want to place a child with a family
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,之后再有这样的事情来破坏这个家庭\N{\fs12}and then have something like this disrupt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,最好还是先把一切都解决好\N{\fs12}lt's better to have all the cards on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那就这样定\N{\fs12}Okay. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你正在用不正当的手段来影响康纳先生的意愿\N{\fs12}You're contesting Mr. Connor's will on the basis of undue influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,里特尔小姐  和一个大她两倍的男人成为情侣\N{\fs12}Miss Little... used a romantic relationship with a man twice her age
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,以此来影响他的遗产规划\N{\fs12}to, uh... influence his estate planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我的委托人和康纳先生是真爱\N{\fs12}My client was in love with Mr. Connor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在他生病期间一直照顾他\N{\fs12}She cared for him during his long illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你的委托人是在操控一个精神脆弱的垂死的老人\N{\fs12}Your client manipulated a dying man who was mentally frail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而你们正提供一百万的慈善捐款\N{\fs12}You're holding up a million-dollar charitable contribution
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给一个非营利机构  - 不  不是这样的  阿尔文\N{\fs12}- to a not-for-profit agency. - No. No, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我的委托人在就遗产问题起诉\N{\fs12}My client is suing Mr. Connor's estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那现在  如果你的委托人想要索赔  你知道的\N{\fs12}Now... if your client wants to file a claim, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她可以等着\N{\fs12}she's free to get in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你只能等着了\N{\fs12}You'll just have to wait it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是他们的目的了\N{\fs12}That's exactly what they want me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道我现在有麻烦\N{\fs12}They know I'm in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,联盟极有可能在解决完遗产问题前就垮掉\N{\fs12}That the Alliance could go under before this is resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那你需要多少钱才能维持\N{\fs12}How much do you need to keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持到年底还需要五万美金吧\N{\fs12}Fifty grand to keep me going till the end of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在聚会上能凑齐吗\N{\fs12}Will you make that from the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你指的是今天上午我们提到的那个聚会吗\N{\fs12}You mean the party that l threw together this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,能有二十个人到我就很满足了\N{\fs12}I'll be lucky if I can get twenty people to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,往好的方向想想\N{\fs12}Oh, it might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,靠一个化装舞会\N{\fs12}A masquerade party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能是世界上最蠢的人了\N{\fs12}I gotta be the dumbest person on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  你不是  - 我甚至都付不起焦油坑的场地费\N{\fs12}- You're not. - I can't even afford The Tar Pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  里特尔小姐\N{\fs12}Alvin. Miss Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  尼克  - 我们认识吗\N{\fs12}- Nick. - Have we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  尼克  是律所的志愿者\N{\fs12}Uh... Nick, uh... volunteers at the Clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他是  巴顿的儿子\N{\fs12}He's, uh... he's Burton's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  嗨\N{\fs12}Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这个了吗\N{\fs12}You see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看过了\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,莱恩·盖金和肯·波特  还记得他们吗\N{\fs12}Len Getkin and Ken Potter. Remember them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,推销员  欠我们大概三万\N{\fs12}Merchandising guys. Owe us about thirty grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我给他们提了个主意  在所有商品上加一个标语\N{\fs12}Right. Well, I sold them on an idea. A slogan for all that merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,信任\N{\fs12}''Believe.''
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好主意  - 是啊\N{\fs12}- Good for you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  而且  我跟露露的助理聊到了周六的化装舞会\N{\fs12}Oh, and I spoke to, uh, Lulu's assistant about that masquerade party on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听起来会有意思  - 是的\N{\fs12}- Sounds like a lotta fun. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我就职于一家叫领军制造的公司\N{\fs12}I work for a company called Principal Products.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他们希望能得到你的作品的使用授权  用于T恤和帽子等\N{\fs12}They're interested in licensing your art... for, uh... for T-shirts, hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,使用授权\N{\fs12}Licensing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们希望能付你一些费用\N{\fs12}They want to... they want to pay you money
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,之后把你的作品放到他们的产品上  比如T恤\N{\fs12}to use your art to apply to their products, like on a T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想要把它放在衣服上\N{\fs12}They want to put it on a... a T-shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就是这个意思  - 然后他们想把衣服卖掉\N{\fs12}- Exactly. - And then they want to sell the T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你的想法  呃\N{\fs12}Well, your message is, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现在非常重要  其他一切都已经准备就绪\N{\fs12}well, it's very important right now, things being the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我不太明白  关于销售的部分\N{\fs12}I'm... I'm not, uh, sure about the, uh... selling part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,墨菲先生  关于那部分\N{\fs12}Well, Mr. Murphy, the... the deal, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在销售之前就会付给你足够一年生活的费用\N{\fs12}There's enough money up-front to cover your living expenses for a year.
