Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还会有更多的钱  也许是足够你舒服过完一辈子的\N{\fs12}well, there might be enough money to keep you comfortable for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,信任\N{\fs12}Believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我的客户想通过你的俱乐部来提高艾滋病的意识\N{\fs12}My client's trying to get into your sports club to increase AIDS awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一周只会来两次\N{\fs12}And they're only interested in coming twice a week
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,发一下避孕套并且做一些免费的艾滋病检测\N{\fs12}to distribute condoms and provide free AIDS testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  但这并不是人们来这里玩的目的\N{\fs12}Right. See, that's not exactly  why people come to this club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是男性体育俱乐部\N{\fs12}This is a men's athletic club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都是来健身的\N{\fs12}The guys work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也是来享受一些私密的友情\N{\fs12}Enjoy the private camaraderie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,通过这种情感关系  你知道的  互相会传染艾滋\N{\fs12}And by camaraderie, do you mean giving each other AIDS,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还会再传染给他们的妻子  女朋友  和孩子\N{\fs12}which then gets spread to their wives and girlfriends and their children?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道  很多孩子一出生就已经被感染了\N{\fs12}Babies are being born infected. You must know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,女士  我想说  即使你提供了一百万个避孕套和免费测试\N{\fs12}Lady. I mean... you could offer a million condoms and tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这的这些家伙  他们也是不会用的\N{\fs12}The guys here... they're not gonna take 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs12}Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,露露\N{\fs12}Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我就是\N{\fs12}Um... I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs12}l...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我是\N{\fs12}I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,露露  你还好吗\N{\fs12}Lulu, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想做一个母亲  真的  但是  现在真的不是一个合适的时机\N{\fs12}I want to be a mother, I do... but, uh... now is just not really the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  尼克他  呃\N{\fs12}And, uh... Nick, is, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我弄不懂他\N{\fs12}He's so unreadable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我并不清楚他是不是也这样想的\N{\fs12}l... l... I'm not really sure that he really wants to do this anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  你爱他吗\N{\fs12}I mean, do you love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我是爱他的\N{\fs12}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可能大部分时候是爱他的  但是之后\N{\fs12}Uh... most of the time I do, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,理解\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这感觉真的很奇怪  你知道吗\N{\fs12}This is really weird... you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  真不敢相信  我就这样全都跟你说了\N{\fs12}I mean, I just... I can't believe I'm... I'm dumping all this on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是\N{\fs12}You were just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,错误的时间  错误的地点\N{\fs12}Wrong place at the wrong time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们并不是特别了解彼此\N{\fs12}We don't know each other very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我们互相是了解的  露露\N{\fs12}We... we know each other, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  你知道  我经常觉得你有一点\N{\fs12}Um... you know, I guess I always thought that you were kind of--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  不  - 别打断我  我只是想说\N{\fs12}- No, no. - Wait, but I just want to say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我希望你能注意安全\N{\fs12}Uh... I hope you're being careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  我是天主教徒  而且是工人阶级\N{\fs12}You know, I was... I was raised Catholic and, uh... and working class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  请理解我的话有些那方面的色彩\N{\fs12}So, uh, understand what I'm about to say is gonna be kinda colored by that.
