Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你会是一个特别好的妈妈\N{\fs12}You're gonna be a wonderful mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而且尼克  尽管他\N{\fs12}And Nick, despite his, uh... his, uh...
