Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是尼克会是一个很可靠的父亲\N{\fs12}Nick's gonna be a solid dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲  呃\N{\fs12}Dad, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有你妈妈的订婚戒指吗\N{\fs12}you still have Mom's engagement ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,当然有\N{\fs12}Yeah. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  如果  呃  如果\N{\fs12}Well, if, uh... if...
