Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 路易莎·阿切尔  - 在这\N{\fs12}- Louisa Archer? - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们准备好了\N{\fs12}They're ready. Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我可以进去吗\N{\fs12}Uh... it's okay if I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你还是在外边等我吧\N{\fs12}I think you should stay here.
