Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可以吗  - 好吧\N{\fs12}- Okay? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉里·瓦伦汀\N{\fs12}Carrie Valentine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\fs12}How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  已经五周了\N{\fs12}Uh... well, I'm five weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,五周了吗\N{\fs12}Five weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  还很早  尼克\N{\fs12}Yeah. It's really early, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,已经五周了\N{\fs12}lt's five weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在它还只是一些小细胞\N{\fs12}lt's just a cluster of cells right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一些小细胞\N{\fs12}Just a little cluster of cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦\N{\fs12}- Oh...
