Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在做什么  - 在拉你的衣服\N{\fs12}- What are you doing? - Pulling your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你怎么在这\N{\fs12}Right. You supposed to be in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘\N{\fs12}Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到艾塔了\N{\fs12}I can't find Etta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我也没看到她\N{\fs12}Oh, l... haven't seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  小宝贝\N{\fs12}Hi, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  -嗨\N{\fs12}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,马库斯正在外边搭一个城堡  要去帮帮他吗\N{\fs12}Marcus is outside making a castle. Do you want to help him?
