Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,艾塔的HIV检测成阳性\N{\fs12}Etta's HIV-positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那马库斯呢\N{\fs12}What about Marcus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他没问题\N{\fs12}Marcus is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是原本想领养他们的家庭已经不行了\N{\fs12}But, the family that was interested in fostering them is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我需要给他们找一个新的地方\N{\fs12}So I need to find a new placement,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  你要知道  能接纳一个四岁的艾滋病患儿的家庭并不多\N{\fs12}but, you know, there's not a lot for a four-year-old with HIV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉自己把一切都搞砸了\N{\fs12}I guess I screwed the whole thing up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,用桌子上那些烂纸把一切都搞砸了\N{\fs12}with that whole... with the cards on the freaking table thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你的问题\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她只是一个那么可爱的小女孩\N{\fs12}She's just such a sweet little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁愿在她做检查之前先让那个家庭了解她\N{\fs12}I wish I'd let the family get to know her before I had her tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不  是因为我的问题\N{\fs12}No, it was my call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是\N{\fs12}No it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我找到了他们的爸爸  - 他在哪\N{\fs12}- I found the dad. - Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他在晨间高地那一个专门为艾滋病人提供的寄宿公寓\N{\fs12}He's at a boarding house in Morningside for people with AIDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,麦先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Wheat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,麦先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Wheat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,麦先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Wheat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,门是开着的\N{\fs12}The door's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不想吃东西了\N{\fs12}Don't want to eat today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我们今天来的目的\N{\fs12}That's not what we're here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么吃的都不要\N{\fs12}Don't want any food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是来发吃的的  麦先生\N{\fs12}We're not here to deliver food, Mr. Wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫苏珊·佩尔  是一名社会工作者\N{\fs12}My name is Suzanne Pell, and I'm a social worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是尼克·法林  他是一名律师\N{\fs12}And this is Nick Fallin. He's a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是想来跟你聊一下你的孩子艾塔和马库斯的\N{\fs12}We're here about your children Etta and Marcus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我妻子在哪\N{\fs12}Where is my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你的妻子四天前已经去世了\N{\fs12}Your wife passed away four days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她死了\N{\fs12}She died?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要为你的孩子们找一个新家\N{\fs12}We need to find a home for your children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮不上什么忙\N{\fs12}I'm... I'm no good for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,麦先生  我们有一些问题\N{\fs12}Mr. Wheat, we have some problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,问题  什么问题  关于我的孩子吗\N{\fs12}Problems? What, with my kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  艾塔是一个艾滋病患者  我们需要给她找一个家\N{\fs12}Yes. Etta is HIV-positive, and we need to find her a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道谁有可能领养他的吗\N{\fs12}Do you know anyone who might take her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,马库斯也是吗\N{\fs12}ls Marcus sick, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我妻子  她是死于艾滋吗\N{\fs12}My wife... she died from the AIDS?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  先生  她是死于艾滋病\N{\fs12}Yes, sir. Yes, she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得是我造成这一切的吗\N{\fs12}You think I did this to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我就把我名片放这边了\N{\fs12}Um... I'm just gonna leave our information here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,黑人本来应该是很强壮的\N{\fs12}Black men are supposed to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是合格的父亲\N{\fs12}Supposed to be fathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉打扰你了\N{\fs12}Sorry to disturb you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我已经结婚了  而且我很爱我的妻子\N{\fs12}l... was a married man... and I loved my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很爱我的孩子\N{\fs12}And I loved my kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个男人  你明白吗\N{\fs12}I was a man, you get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那么一万美元  立即支付\N{\fs12}So ten thousand dollars, payable immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,再加上出售后收入的百分之二\N{\fs12}Plus two percent of the adjusted gross revenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是一笔划算的买卖\N{\fs12}lt's... it's a good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fs12}Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs12}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不要做红色的T恤\N{\fs12}No red T-shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因为太阳的颜色  当然了\N{\fs12}Because the color of the sun, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  同理也不要做橙色的\N{\fs12}And, uh... no orange for the same reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还有  不要做高领毛衣\N{\fs12}And, uh... no turtlenecks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs12}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,仅限二号铅笔\N{\fs12}Number 2 pencils only.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也不要做书包或者午餐盒\N{\fs12}And no backpacks or lunchboxes.
