Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs12}Ah--
