Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  不能做钥匙链\N{\fs12}Wha... No key chains?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有一些人\N{\fs12}S-Some people...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人他们不用钥匙\N{\fs12}Some people don't have keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  呃\N{\fs12}And, uh... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要在周一卖这些东西\N{\fs12}no selling of these products on Mondays.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要让一周在轻松愉快中开始\N{\fs12}We have to let the week begin easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  墨菲先生  你说的这些都很有意思\N{\fs12}Well, Mr. Murphy, uh... all this is very interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是恐怕你的要求都不能被答应\N{\fs12}but I'm afraid none of your requests can be granted.
