Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这个还是可以理解的\N{\fs12}which does kinda make some sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那我们就这样说定了\N{\fs12}Okay, so we're agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那一万美金的独家许可权费用\N{\fs12}Then ten thousand dollars for exclusive licensing rights
