Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  不能做红色或橙色\N{\fs12}No. No orange or red.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不做橙色和红色\N{\fs12}No orange or red.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不做橙色和红色\N{\fs12}No orange or red.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不做橙色和红色\N{\fs12}No orange or red.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.81,0:21:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fs12}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  那么  我就开始商标核名了\N{\fs12}Okay, so I'll... I'll get the trademark search started.
