Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:21:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,巴顿\N{\fs12}Burton?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  阿尔文  最近怎么样\N{\fs12}Hey, Alvin. How are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那个起草沃伦·康纳遗嘱的律师\N{\fs12}The, uh, lawyer who, uh, drafted Warren Connor's wilI's gonna testify
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,将会证明沃伦没有反复修改文件\N{\fs12}that Warren was not unduly influenced to revise the document.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我向法庭提出了这项动议  要求驳回诉求\N{\fs12}So I filed a motion with the Orphan's Court to have the contest dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,听证会定于下周进行\N{\fs12}The hearing's scheduled for next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会出席的\N{\fs12}We'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  一百万美元  没了它  很多人会死\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin. A million dollars. Without it, people will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,饱受饥饿的艾滋病患者会连一口热饭都没有\N{\fs12}People with AIDS who are hungry won't receive hot meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.38,0:22:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,会没有处方药\N{\fs12}They won't get their prescription drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,里特尔小姐  我清楚你是好心的\N{\fs12}Miss Little, I'm... I'm sure your intentions are... the best,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.21,0:22:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但这也是一个家庭的问题\N{\fs12}but this is... this is a family matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.25,0:22:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我这周能通过这个聚会筹集五万\N{\fs12}lf I could just get fifty grand out of the party this weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.04,0:22:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就还能再坚持三十天\N{\fs12}I could hold out for another thirty days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我有时间\N{\fs12}Well... I have some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我是一个很厉害的筹款人\N{\fs12}And I'm a pretty good fundraiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们可以  呃  集思广益\N{\fs12}Maybe we could, uh... brainstorm some ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有关心过沃伦\N{\fs12}I never really cared for Warren.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是么\N{\fs12}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,让这种男人做些好事的唯一方法\N{\fs12}The only way to get a man like that to do something good
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就是和他上床\N{\fs12}was to... sleep with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我这样做的原因\N{\fs12}That's why I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥哥十年前死于艾滋\N{\fs12}My brother died of AIDS... ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,匹兹堡有数千人需要帮助\N{\fs12}There are thousand of people in Pittsburgh who need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我会竭尽所能\N{\fs12}I do what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我很不好意思\N{\fs12}I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,其实  我喜欢你\N{\fs12}Look... I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不想让你觉得  我是真的关心他\N{\fs12}I don't want you to think that... l... I did care about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.39,0:23:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很了解彼此\N{\fs12}We knew each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.57,0:23:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  这很复杂\N{\fs12}But... it was complica--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.95,0:24:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.97,0:24:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  -请进\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.01,0:24:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\fs12}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.02,0:24:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,路过银行 拿上戒指\N{\fs12}Went by the bank. Picked up the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.65,0:24:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我1965年用全部身家买的\N{\fs12}lt's all I could afford in 1965.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.68,0:24:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,将近一克拉\N{\fs12}lt's almost a carat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.82,0:24:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在我印象中应该更大一点\N{\fs12}I remember it being a little bigger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.01,0:24:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮\N{\fs12}lt's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.68,0:24:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  是你妈妈选的  你知道吗\N{\fs12}Actually, your mother picked it out, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.27,0:24:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,她总是领先我一步\N{\fs12}She was always a step ahead of me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.23,0:24:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她说她不想我给她惊喜  所以她自己选了一个\N{\fs12}She told me she didn't want me to surprise her, so she picked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.29,0:25:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  当我向你妈妈求婚的时候\N{\fs12}You know, when I proposed to your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.56,0:25:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她  其实早就知道  但是  她表现的特别惊讶\N{\fs12}she... she was expecting it anyway, but she, uh... she acted surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.29,0:25:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  不管怎样  呃  我  我都想祝福你\N{\fs12}Well, anyway, uh... l... I want to wish you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.21,0:25:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  我很爱你的妈妈\N{\fs12}Nicholas, I loved your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.74,0:25:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能明白\N{\fs12}I hope you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.97,0:25:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想一辈子都能和她在一起\N{\fs12}I wanted to spend my life with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.84,0:25:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是事情就是不能如意  所以  我  我放手了\N{\fs12}Things just... fell apart, and l... l... I let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.31,0:25:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我放手了\N{\fs12}I let... I let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.24,0:25:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我很遗憾\N{\fs12}I regret that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.04,0:25:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fs12}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.04,0:25:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你会做得更好\N{\fs12}you'll do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.50,0:25:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你  孩子\N{\fs12}I love you, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.66,0:26:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱你  爸爸\N{\fs12}I love you, too, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.52,0:26:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,斯坦利高地集体救助所\N{\fs12}Stanley Heights Group Shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.06,0:26:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这是唯一一个可以接受艾滋病患儿的地方\N{\fs12}lt's the only shelter that can handle HIV-positive children.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.94,0:26:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少十岁以下的孩子住在那\N{\fs12}How many kids under ten live there?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.76,0:26:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 并不多  - 好吧\N{\fs12}- Not many. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.88,0:26:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我检查了县里的每一张床\N{\fs12}I've checked every bed in the county.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.02,0:26:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  我们可以分开他们  但是艾塔还是要去斯坦利高地\N{\fs12}I mean, we could split them up, but Etta's still gonna have to go to Stanley Heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.32,0:26:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  哦  嗨  苏珊\N{\fs12}Nick. Oh, hi, Suzanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.08,0:26:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有几个关于麦的案子的人想要见你\N{\fs12}There's a couple here to see you regarding the Wheat case.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.02,0:26:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在整个悲剧发生之前  达里尔认识凯文·麦\N{\fs12}Daryl used to know Calvin Wheat before the whole tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.93,0:26:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他们之前一起在体育馆打篮球\N{\fs12}They played basketball together at the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.61,0:26:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.39,0:26:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天凯文给我打电话的时候我正在上班\N{\fs12}I was at work yesterday when I got the call from Calvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.08,0:26:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经很多年没跟他联系了\N{\fs12}I hadn't... talked to him in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.44,0:26:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟我说了关于他的孩子的问题\N{\fs12}He told me about the problems with his children.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.93,0:26:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他们没有能去的合适的地方\N{\fs12}That... they didn't have any place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.87,0:27:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小艾塔还生病了\N{\fs12}That little Etta was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.82,0:27:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我跟妮可说了这件事\N{\fs12}So I talked to Nicole about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.83,0:27:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为此祈祷  并且\N{\fs12}And we prayed about it and...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.49,0:27:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上我们决定\N{\fs12}And this morning we decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.67,0:27:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做是对的\N{\fs12}This is the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.76,0:27:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,莱基先生莱基太太  你们清楚艾塔会有一些特殊需求吗\N{\fs12}Mr. and Mrs. Lakey, you understand that Etta has special needs?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.44,0:27:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你们准备好接受关于这类疾病的教育了吗\N{\fs12}And you're prepared to educate yourself about the disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.77,0:27:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  我们并不太了解艾滋病\N{\fs12}We don't know much about it. It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.07,0:27:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们可以学习\N{\fs12}But we can learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.02,0:27:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.23,0:27:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  既然你们已经来了  那需要你们填写这份文件\N{\fs12}Well, while you're here, we'll have you fill out the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.47,0:27:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们将在今天晚些时候安排家庭学习和医疗评估\N{\fs12}And then we'll schedule a home study and medical evaluations for later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.22,0:27:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fs12}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.37,0:27:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那好的\N{\fs12}Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.86,0:27:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们什么时候可以见一见孩子们\N{\fs12}When can we see the kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.91,0:27:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.15,0:27:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.56,0:27:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  卫生检查员说\N{\fs12}Oh, the health inspector said...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.94,0:27:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  你让给我们进行突然采访的家伙\N{\fs12}Oh... that guy you had pay us a surprise visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.56,0:28:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.59,0:28:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那个发现我们符合标准的家伙\N{\fs12}The guy who found our facilities up to code.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.13,0:28:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  他说你在等我\N{\fs12}Right. He said you'd be expecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.22,0:28:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我带来了避孕套\N{\fs12}So... I have the condoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.78,0:28:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,右边那扇门\N{\fs12}That door on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.37,0:28:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把他们和其他的都放在这\N{\fs12}You can put it in here with the rest of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.84,0:28:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  放在这没人会看到\N{\fs12}No. No one's gonna see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.37,0:28:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是要随身带着这些东西\N{\fs12}Then take them with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.00,0:28:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思  我没明白\N{\fs12}Know what? I don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.86,0:28:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我所希望的就是你能给大家一个安全的选择\N{\fs12}All I'm asking is that you give people the option to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.74,0:28:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道  这是为了阻止一些事情的发生\N{\fs12}You know, stop an avoidable thing from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.50,0:28:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我没时间应付这些\N{\fs12}Okay. I don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.07,0:28:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,扔在这  或者带着走  随便你\N{\fs12}Leave them. Take them. It's your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.50,0:28:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,随便我\N{\fs12}My call?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.88,0:28:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是这个意思  随便你  女士\N{\fs12}That's what I just said. It's all up to you, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.63,0:28:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想把这些扔进一个脏兮兮的壁橱里\N{\fs12}And they wanted to just toss them in some moldy closet
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.42,0:28:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他们扔其他避孕套和艾滋病资料的地方\N{\fs12}where they hide all of their condoms and AIDS literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.36,0:28:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这个让你觉得可能\N{\fs12}And so this makes you think that maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.63,0:29:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  也许我只是因为自己的感受\N{\fs12}Yeah. Maybe I'm just looking for all the bad things
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.26,0:29:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看到的都是不好的方面\N{\fs12}to justify the way that I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.67,0:29:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.93,0:29:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.44,0:29:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs12}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.13,0:29:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  是的\N{\fs12}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.49,0:29:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  打电话给欧盟的人\N{\fs12}No, no, no. Just call the European Union guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.08,0:29:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  这样就可以\N{\fs12}Right. It... it's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.38,0:29:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你能处理好的\N{\fs12}You can get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.08,0:29:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.09,0:29:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  只是  尽职地调查关于  信任  的事情\N{\fs12}Just, uh... due diligence on this ''Believe'' thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.97,0:29:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呃  你需要去处理这件事吗  - 不用\N{\fs12}- Oh, you need to take care of it? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.41,0:29:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你说的是战争  贫穷  艾滋病  那为什么要把孩子卷进来\N{\fs12}So, uhm... you were saying, war, poverty, AIDS... Why bring a kid into that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.40,0:29:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢\N{\fs12}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.71,0:29:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  当我妈妈企图自杀的时候  她\N{\fs12}You know, when my mother attempted suicide, she, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.88,0:29:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我觉得  她  她特别沮丧\N{\fs12}Well, I mean, she... she got very depressed and...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.75,0:29:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就做了一些傻事\N{\fs12}and then she did something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.54,0:29:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs12}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.86,0:29:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  她并不是真的想死\N{\fs12}Well, she didn't really want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.97,0:29:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她只是害怕了\N{\fs12}She was afraid, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.84,0:29:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  如果你要问我的看法\N{\fs12}I mean, if you're asking my opinion...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.97,0:29:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我怎么想的\N{\fs12}you know what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.67,0:30:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  嘿  有时间吗\N{\fs12}Oh, hey. You got a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.24,0:30:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我正要回家\N{\fs12}No, I'm trying to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.52,0:30:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 莱基一家通过了他们的家庭学习  - 很好\N{\fs12}- The Lakeys passed their home study. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.19,0:30:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是到医疗检测时  莱基先生拒绝做血液检测\N{\fs12}But at the medical exam, Mr. Lakey refused to take the blood test.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.35,0:30:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他拒绝做血液检测  - 是的\N{\fs12}- He refused his blood test? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.05,0:30:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的意思是  这是他的权利  但是我  - 好吧\N{\fs12}- I mean, it's within his rights, but l-- - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.29,0:30:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在这种情况下  - 好的  我会再了解一下\N{\fs12}- Under the circumstances-- - Yeah, I'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.28,0:30:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我得回家了\N{\fs12}I gotta get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.17,0:30:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,今天怎么样\N{\fs12}How was your day?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.61,0:30:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还不错\N{\fs12}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.76,0:30:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那很好啊\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.82,0:30:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\fs12}Yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.06,0:30:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也挺好\N{\fs12}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.18,0:30:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.12,0:30:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们真的要戴面具去这个聚会吗\N{\fs12}Do you think we really have to wear masks to this party?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.59,0:30:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.32,0:30:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不知道哪里\N{\fs12}'Cause I just don't know where...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.40,0:30:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我想   我们也许可以戴万圣节的面具\N{\fs12}I mean, I guess we could wear Halloween masks,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.35,0:30:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不认为这是他们想得到的效果\N{\fs12}but I don't think that's what they have in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.10,0:30:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.21,0:30:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  你吃饭了吗\N{\fs12}Um... did you eat anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.83,0:30:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还没\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.23,0:30:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那  冰箱里还有半个三明治\N{\fs12}Well, there's a half a sandwich in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.15,0:31:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们面临着一个更大的抉择  尼克\N{\fs12}We have a much bigger decision in front of us, Nick,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.65,0:31:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  比结婚更重要的\N{\fs12}than getting married, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.77,0:31:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要做一个更加重要的决定\N{\fs12}We have a much... much bigger decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.28,0:31:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样  我并不想只是因为怀孕了就结婚\N{\fs12}I don't want to get married just because I'm pregnant... anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.36,0:31:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太明白你\N{\fs12}I just don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.61,0:31:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你为什么不跟我谈这件事\N{\fs12}I don't know why you didn't talk to me about this, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.50,0:32:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我谈谈你正考虑做什么样的改变\N{\fs12}Just talk to me about what you're thinking for a change
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.77,0:32:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,因为  这并不需要多么浪漫\N{\fs12}because... this doesn't have to be romantic-- our thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.77,0:32:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道  我们应该像成年人一样\N{\fs12}You know, we really should be like adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.66,0:32:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该好好谈谈然后做出决定\N{\fs12}and we should talk about things and then make decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.29,0:32:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fs12}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.39,0:32:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我  如果你不想嫁给我  我并不会介意\N{\fs12}l... I don't... I don't care if you don't want to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.73,0:32:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的  我只是  你知道\N{\fs12}lt's all right. I just... You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.55,0:32:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我已经准备好做一个父亲了\N{\fs12}I know that I'm ready to be a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.29,0:32:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我确定\N{\fs12}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.06,0:32:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,帽子真好看\N{\fs12}lt's a really nice hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.53,0:32:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我相信\N{\fs12}Yeah. I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.75,0:32:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我收到了一封芝加哥律师事务所的信\N{\fs12}So... I received a letter from the Chicago law firm
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.66,0:32:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,代表了富山清酒的利益\N{\fs12}that represents Fujiyama Sake's U.S. interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.19,0:32:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,富山清酒的最高端产品就叫做信任\N{\fs12}Fujiyama's top shelf Sake is called Believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.00,0:33:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,信任清酒\N{\fs12}Believe Sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.92,0:33:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,其中文字是被红色的太阳包围的\N{\fs12}The text of which is surrounded by a red sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.45,0:33:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我们现在面临这个问题\N{\fs12}So... we have this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.52,0:33:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fs12}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.96,0:33:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们  他们威胁将会提起联邦诉讼\N{\fs12}Well, they're... they're threatening a Federal lawsuit
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.10,0:33:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们使用他们的商标\N{\fs12}if we use their trademark.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.71,0:33:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经打印了七万五千件产品\N{\fs12}We printed seventy-five thousand of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.56,0:33:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不会同意\N{\fs12}I never give you the go-ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.97,0:33:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉我们要动作快\N{\fs12}You told us to act fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.73,0:33:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我很抱歉  你们不能卖这些T恤和帽子\N{\fs12}Well... I'm sorry, you can't sell the T-shirts or the hats
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.32,0:33:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,或者  或者钥匙链\N{\fs12}or the... or the key chains.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.21,0:33:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样\N{\fs12}How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.55,0:33:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有重要明确的指示\N{\fs12}There were no significant indicators.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.79,0:33:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有检查日本的商标吗\N{\fs12}You... you didn't check Japan for trademarks?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.39,0:33:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我查了文字和字母  并没有什么明确的问题\N{\fs12}Well, I ran the text and the letters, and nothing significant came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.30,0:33:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有查日本的吗\N{\fs12}You didn't check Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.98,0:33:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们不能给我钱\N{\fs12}So they can't give me the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.55,0:33:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这家叫富士清酒的公司\N{\fs12}Because of this company, Fujiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.76,0:33:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,富士清酒\N{\fs12}Fujiyama Sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.10,0:33:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷德  你知道富士清酒是什么吗\N{\fs12}Do... do you know what Fujiyama Sake is, Fred?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.18,0:33:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我知道清酒  上帝清酒\N{\fs12}Well, I know what Sake is, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.77,0:33:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经住在日本\N{\fs12}I lived in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.09,0:33:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你在日本待过\N{\fs12}You... you were in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.56,0:33:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当时参军  曾经住在日本\N{\fs12}When I was in the Army, I lived in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.02,0:33:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我在日本的时候  会喝清酒  所有人都喝的\N{\fs12}When I was in Japan, I drank Sake. Everyone drinks Sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.55,0:34:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.59,0:34:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,麦先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Wheat?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.88,0:34:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  怎么了\N{\fs12}Yeah, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.57,0:34:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我两天前就来这了\N{\fs12}I came by here two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.30,0:34:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子们都还好吗\N{\fs12}Are my kids okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.47,0:34:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,达里尔·莱基\N{\fs12}Daryl Lakey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.49,0:34:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.09,0:34:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你能跟我解释清楚吗\N{\fs12}Can you help me understand something?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.01,0:34:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.22,0:34:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你和他有关系吗\N{\fs12}Were you involved with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.17,0:34:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\fs12}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.21,0:34:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你和他做过吗  他  是你的伴侣之一吗\N{\fs12}Did you have sex with him? Was he... was he one of your partners?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.44,0:34:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,麦先生  这就是我想了解的\N{\fs12}See, here's my problem, Mr. Wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.15,0:34:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我把你的孩子们送到莱基家生活\N{\fs12}lf I give your children to the Lakeys
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.91,0:34:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,而且如果莱基先生是艾滋病患者而莱基夫人并不知情\N{\fs12}and if Mr. Lakey's HIV-positive and if Mrs. Lakey doesn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.65,0:34:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那么就又有一个家庭要被毁了\N{\fs12}then another family will be destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.82,0:35:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,而你的孩子们又被卷入其中\N{\fs12}with your children in the middle of it... again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.48,0:35:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,莱基先生  我请您独自过来的原因\N{\fs12}Mr. Lakey, the reason I asked you to come in here by yourself--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.80,0:35:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我们单独聊一会吗\N{\fs12}Can you leave us a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.73,0:35:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.21,0:35:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我和凯文·麦先生聊过了\N{\fs12}I spoke with Calvin Wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.69,0:35:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.86,0:35:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,由于你拒绝做血液检测  所以我去找了他\N{\fs12}I went to see him because of your refusal to give a blood sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.44,0:35:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.24,0:35:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他证实了一些事情\N{\fs12}He confirmed some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.96,0:35:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  我是不会做血液测试的\N{\fs12}I don't take blood tests, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.91,0:35:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么最初有像凯文一样的黑人会得病\N{\fs12}That's how black men get diseases like Calvin's in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.33,0:35:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,凯文·麦并不是从针头感染艾滋的  是吧\N{\fs12}Calvin Wheat didn't contract HIV from a needle, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.38,0:35:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他怎么得的\N{\fs12}I don't know how he got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.52,0:35:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.87,0:35:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,莱基先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Lakey,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.63,0:35:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在做的事情  照顾他的孩子们这件事  是一件好事\N{\fs12}what you're doing, taking in his children, is a very good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.58,0:35:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果你是艾滋病人  而且如果你感染给你的\N{\fs12}But if you're HIV-positive and then if you infect your--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.64,0:36:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我闭嘴\N{\fs12}You shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.60,0:36:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是同性恋  所以你最好给我闭嘴\N{\fs12}I am not a faggot... so you shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.67,0:36:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我在努力做一些好事  法林先生\N{\fs12}I am trying to do the right thing here, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.32,0:36:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好别逼我改变主意\N{\fs12}But don't make me change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.27,0:36:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗\N{\fs12}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.67,0:36:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,别逼我改变主意\N{\fs12}Don't make me change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.55,0:36:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做什么\N{\fs12}What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.98,0:36:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的建议\N{\fs12}lt's your recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.09,0:36:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你的安置计划\N{\fs12}Your placement.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.94,0:36:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,总比在斯坦利高地好\N{\fs12}lt's better than Stanley Heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.02,0:36:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,希望如此吧\N{\fs12}Hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.37,0:36:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,太复杂了\N{\fs12}lt's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.24,0:37:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.17,0:37:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.32,0:37:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,事情顺利吗\N{\fs12}How are things?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.80,0:37:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还不错  还不错  - 那就好\N{\fs12}- Fine. Fine. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.67,0:37:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要些什么吗\N{\fs12}Do you need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.94,0:37:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就想知道事情进展怎么样\N{\fs12}Just wanted to know how things went.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.43,0:37:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还没求婚呢\N{\fs12}Haven't done it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.86,0:37:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs12}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.65,0:37:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是想让大家都知道\N{\fs12}I just want to let everybody know
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.48,0:37:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经筹到一半了——两万六千美元\N{\fs12}we've reached our halmay point-- twenty-six thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.18,0:37:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  请慷慨解囊\N{\fs12}So please, empty out your pockets,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.20,0:37:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出信用卡  捐赠  捐赠  再捐赠\N{\fs12}put it on the credit card, and give, give, give.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.10,0:38:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我感觉并不怎么好\N{\fs12}You know... I don't... I don't feel so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.47,0:38:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是需要一些水或者其他东西\N{\fs12}Maybe... Do you... do you want some more water or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.81,0:38:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  不需要了\N{\fs12}Oh, no. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.06,0:38:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们需要点新鲜空气或者\N{\fs12}Maybe we need some air or...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.69,0:38:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我想我们还回家了\N{\fs12}lt's okay. I think I'm just gonna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.29,0:38:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是的   我们该回家了\N{\fs12}Yeah. Let's... Iet's just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.24,0:38:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好好玩  - 好的\N{\fs12}- Have fun. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.46,0:38:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 失陪了  - 晚安\N{\fs12}- Sorry. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.51,0:38:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fs12}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.76,0:38:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你知道吗\N{\fs12}Hey, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.40,0:38:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前答应过要帮忙的  所以你应该留下来的\N{\fs12}You should just stay because you promised you'd help with the ramle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.80,0:38:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦  其他人做就行了  - 不  不 不行\N{\fs12}- Oh, someone else can do it. - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.43,0:38:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就留下来吧  我自己回家\N{\fs12}Just... just stay, please. I'm... I'm gonna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.73,0:38:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事  我就是要回家了\N{\fs12}I'm fine. I just need to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.17,0:38:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,晚点见\N{\fs12}I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.15,0:38:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.40,0:38:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我们十名幸运获奖者中的一个\N{\fs12}Now for the first of our ten lucky winners
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.51,0:38:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,获得漂亮的陶瓷小丑玩偶\N{\fs12}of this beautiful ceramic jester doll,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.75,0:38:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,由林肯大街隐藏宝藏捐赠\N{\fs12}donated by Hidden Treasures on Lincoln Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.88,0:38:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,4084\N{\fs12}4084.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.35,0:38:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,号码是4084的朋友  请上台来领取你的奖品\N{\fs12}Whoever has ticket 4084, come on up and get your prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.61,0:39:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得娃娃都是用报纸包起来的\N{\fs12}I think the dolls are wrapped in newspaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.69,0:39:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,或者在下面一个大纸板箱里\N{\fs12}or they're in a big cardboard box, down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.65,0:39:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,祝贺\N{\fs12}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.81,0:39:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hi.
